Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是创造与毁灭的大熔炉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a crucible of creation and destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"银河"这名字听上去的感觉…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The name "Milky Way" sounds like something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒心 恬静\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}kind of comforting and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而银河系却是个怪物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the Milky Way galaxy is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是数十亿个星系中的一个而我们处在其边缘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's just one galaxy among billions, and we're living on the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前我们发现了两个小星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just recently, we've discovered that there are two small galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前正与银河系发生碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}colliding with the Milky Way right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一条明亮的恒星与大团尘埃组成的挂毯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a tapestry of brilliant suns and blinding dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人惊奇的是从我们相当明亮的银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's surprising how little of the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达我们的光线相当的少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from our rather luminous Milky Way galaxy reaches us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个极端的地方 在这里恒星可以慢吞吞地漂移\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a place of extremes, where stars can drift lazily...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者每小时被甩出百万多英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or be flung out at more than a million miles per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在科学家已经透过星系昏暗的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now scientists have pierced the galaxy's heart of darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找到穿越银河的出路\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to find ourway through the Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,1,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}--==本影片由 {\1c&HFF8000&\b1}CMCT 团队{\fn华文楷体\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0} 荣誉出品==--\N更多精彩影视 请访问 {\fnCronos Pro Subhead\1c&HFF00FF&\b1}http://cmct.cc{\r}
