Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第四集 银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 04of19 Milky.Way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它直径有10万光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's 100,000 light-years in diameter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质量比我们的太阳大万亿倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has a trillion times more mass than our Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它诞生于130亿年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt began about thirteen billion years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前仍然在构建之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and is still under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的星系 银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's our galaxy, the Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河系是一个极其活跃的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Milky Way galaxy is an extremely active place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就像一个建设项目\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's like a construction project.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切一直都在发生变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's things going on all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看到年长的恒星死亡 摧毁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have old stars dying and torn down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这些物质被用来建造全新的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then that material gets used to build brand-new stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个作业区内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the midst of this work zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐落有我们小小的太阳系 还有很多很多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lies our little solar system and a whole lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想最好是将银河系看作是我们的恒星大家庭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l suppose the best way to think of the Milky Way galaxy...is ourfamily of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些成群结伴恒星穿梭在宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are the stars that we travel through the universe with...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都围绕着共同的中心运行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a clump, all orbiting a common center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其展开的螺旋臂里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Within its far-reaching spiral arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏着我们诞生和如何消亡的线索\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lie clues to where we started...and how it all will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晴朗的夏夜 银河系里的群星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On a clear summer night, the stars of the Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像闪闪发光的旗帜展开在夜空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}unfurl like a shimmering banner across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古埃及人将这条星河看作是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ancient Egyptians saw this river of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通往来世的道路\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a pathway to the afterlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而希腊人最先给它取名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the Greeks were the first to name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河来自"galacos"一词\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Milky Way comes from the word "galacos"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希腊语中的牛奶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is Greek for milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管我们曾经以为我们处在宇宙的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And though we once believed we lived at the center of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在我们知道我们甚至都不处于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we now know that we don't even live...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自己星系的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the center of our own galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我们仰望夜空时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we look up into the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到这条乳白色的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we see this milky swath of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将其称为银河的星河\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we call the Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们实际上看到的是银河的旋臂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what we're actually seeing is a spiral arm of the galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它比我们更靠近银河的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's closer to the center of the galaxy than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里并不能真正看到银河的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We can't really see the center of the galaxy from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们能够看到其中的一条旋臂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but what we can see is one of the spiral arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它距离中心比我们近几千光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's a few thousand light-years closer to the center than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们地球这个位置注视银河\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we gaze at the Milky Way from our earthbound position...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像看到硬币的边缘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's like looking at the edge of a coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们感觉不到银河的真实形状\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We get no sense of the galaxy's real shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而假如你从上端俯视星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf, however, you look at a galaxy from the top down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是个圆盘 请记住\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's a disk, remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是从上往下看一个飞碟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it's like looking at a Frisbee from the top down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看到整个光盘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can see its full glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管它很薄但你看不出它的厚薄\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even though it's thin, you don't see how thin it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你可以看到它整个结构\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but you see its full structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以将银河比作一座城市\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can make the analogy of the Milky Way...as being very much like a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是中心区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a central region...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有高大的建筑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's big buildings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间有大量的活动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's a lot of action in the middle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那非常适合于我们的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's certainly true of our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你来到郊区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then you move out to the suburbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的生活多了几分舒适\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where life is a little bit more comfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多了几分轻松\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a little more relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是养家活口的好地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a better place to raise a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我们安家之处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is where we reside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太阳系位于银河系的旋臂内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our solar system is among the Milky Way's spiral arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离热闹的中心2.6万光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}26,000 light-years from the bustling center.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的星系非常的大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our galaxy is so large...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球转上一圈需要2亿多年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it takes Earth more than 200 million years to make one lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳就位于市中心周围的普通街坊内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sun is located in what would be...just an average neighborhood around the city center.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而此外如果你站在这个街坊的中间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But, again, if you stand in the middle of this neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不知道城市另一面的街坊的模样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you don't really know what the neighborhood...on the opposite side of the city looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你无法直接看到它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because you can't see it directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于我们搬出了郊区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we move outward beyond the suburbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人口越发稀少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the population becomes more sparse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你甚至有点偏远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And, yeah, you've even got sort of the boondocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们的星系里你看得到光环\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln our galaxy, you've got the halo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很年老的恒星处在星系很远的轨道上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where you have very old stars...in sort of wide orbits around the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系的伸展不会止步于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The galactic sprawl doesn't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河系松散不定的光环上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the Milky Way's loose and undefined halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它远远超过我们的街坊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt reaches far beyond our neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过了叫做本星系的星系群\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and out to a group of galaxies called the Local Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你把银河系看作洛杉矶这样的城市的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf you think of the Milky Way galaxy...as a city like Los Angeles...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你可以将这些看作是加州内的所有郡县\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then you can think of these as counties all within the state of California.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合在一起这个本星系就组成了整个州\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And together, this Local Group makes up the entire state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我们庞大的银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Besides our huge Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和更大的仙女座星系外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the even larger Andromeda galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本星系由相近的50个较小的星系组成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Local Group consists of close to fifty smaller galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中最近的距离约4万光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the closest of which are roughly 40,000 light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两个相对较近的矮星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are two relatively nearby dwarf galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小麦哲伦星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Large and Small Clouds of Magellan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕着我们的银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that orbit our Milky Way galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在南半球很容易观察到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and are easily seen in the southern hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都是不大的小星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're small, little galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我们的本星系有几十个这样的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But our Local Group has several dozen such galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面到处游荡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sort of wandering around inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大星系是少数民族\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The big galaxies are the minority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实实在在的一个优势是处于我们星系的外缘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One advantage of actually being in the outer edges of our galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以更加清晰地观察到我们银河系外面的世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we have a clearer view of outside of our Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能够看到宇宙的其它部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're able to see the rest of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们邻近的星系和我们本星系以外的星系群\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our neighboring galaxies and galaxy clusters...beyond our own Local Group of galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河系光环内有大量的球状星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnside the Milky Way's halo lie massive globular clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球状星团密密麻麻挤满了恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Globular clusters are densely packed regions of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是同类的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that are all of similar composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些就像银河系里的民族聚居区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are like the ethnic neighborhoods of the Milky Way galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 这些球状星团形成时 银河系还很年强\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lndeed, these globular clusters formed when the galaxy was very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是形成的第一批恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are among the first stars to have formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些星团年龄在120至130亿年间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some globular clusters are twelve or thirteen billion years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们包含了十亿甚至上百亿颗恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They contain a hundred thousand or even a million stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球状星团几乎和宇宙本身一样年长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Globular clusters, almost as old as the universe itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了我们身处星系位置的第一个线索\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}gave us the first clue to our place in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到了天上的这些球状星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We saw these globular clusters in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它们的中心距离我们很远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but their centerwas somewhere far away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们最先测量成果之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that was one of ourfirst measurements...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是在星系的中间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of where the middle of the galaxy should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们并不围绕着我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They weren't orbiting around us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是围绕着2.7万光年以外的某个区域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but around an area somewhere about 27,000 light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从来没有能够足够远地从我们星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We can never get far enough away from our own galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正地看到它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to actually see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而通过观察其他星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But by looking at other galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比对我们对自己星系的了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and comparing what we know about our own galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们获得了银河系相当不错的图像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we've got a pretty good picture of the Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们首次通过望远镜看到星系时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The very first time we saw galaxies through telescopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们甚至都不知道它们是星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we didn't even know they were galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们原以为它们只是我们银河系里的星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We thought they were just nebulae in our own galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是震惊于其美丽的螺旋形状\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we were just amazed by the beautiful spiral shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以自然而然 天文学家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it was sort of natural for astronomers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据我们所见的它们的形态来进行分类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to classify galaxies according to their shape, what we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文学家甄别出了四种基本的星系形态:\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronomers recognize four basic galactic shapes:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椭圆状 由老龄恒星构成并不旋转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Elliptical, built of old stars and which doesn't spin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荚状 包括了凸出部分和圆盘部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lenticular, consisting of a bulge and a disc...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很少甚至没有新的恒星形成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and little or no new starformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不规则状 它完全没有实际的形状\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}irregular, which has no real shape at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如我们本星系里的麦哲伦星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like the Magellanic Clouds in our own Local Group...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋状 包括了我们的银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and spiral, which includes our Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是个年轻和年老的恒星组成的风车\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a pinwheel of young and old stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其中优雅地旋转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}spinning gracefully through space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前人们认为有可能椭圆星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A long time ago, people thought that maybe an elliptical galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后会塌落成螺旋星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}eventually collapses down into a spiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者有可能最终所有的螺旋形系会归拢到一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or maybe eventually spirals all come together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成椭圆星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and form an elliptical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难弄清楚其先后次序究竟是什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it was sort of hard to figure out exactlywhat the sequence is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们清楚的一件事是椭圆星系通常是非常大的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One thing we know is that elliptical galaxies tend to be very large.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半人马座A 一个畸形椭圆星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Centaurus A, a misshapen elliptical galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约在1300万光年以外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about thirteen million light-years away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揭示了椭圆星系会如此之大的原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}suggests why elliptical galaxies get so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有许多证据证明了在那里某个地方有一个螺旋星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a lot of evidence that there's a spiral galaxy in there somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个更大的星系所吸纳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that got absorbed by a larger galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以此刻有可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, right now, it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所见到的这些很大的椭圆星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that these really big elliptical galaxies we see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是几个螺旋星系和其他类型的星系合并而成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may be the mergers of several spirals and other types of galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的银河系短时期内没有被吸纳的危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Milky Way isn't in danger of being absorbed any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们的螺旋星系的核心已经透露了自己的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the heart of our spiral galaxy has revealed a secret of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最近 我们发现银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Only recently, we discovered that the Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非典型的螺旋星系 而是棒旋星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is not a classic spiral, but a barred spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一条群星组成的棒穿过其中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a bar of stars going through the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋臂像是依附在那条棒上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the spiral arms sort of attach offfrom that bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,横跨2.7万光年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Spanning 27,000 light-years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是星系中最普通的棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's the most popular bar in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3000万颗恒星被其吸引\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thirty million stars gravitate to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们星系的棒是万有引力的自然结果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The bar of our galaxy is a natural result of gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个恒星之间的相互引力作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mutual gravitational interactions of the individual stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成了我们星系的圆盘部分和凸起部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that form the disk of our galaxy and the bulge of our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有时会造成恒星挤在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt causes sometimes the stars to sort of bunch up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成这样的棒形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into this bar configuration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河中心的周围是巨大的中心隆起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Surrounding the middle of the Milky Way...is a huge central bulge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成它的主要恒星的年岁在100至110亿年之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's mostly composed of stars between ten and eleven billion years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸起的大小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The size of the bulge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系到银河系整个最扣人心弦的特色\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is linked to the Milky Way's most gripping feature of all...
